{"tid":1142402,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] 點樣可以勸屋企人戒煙？","createTime":"2019-05-07T04:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T13:32:38.000Z","uid":67549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bcdb2b3c25675c5ec890e83984209ebaa2e10a04","tid":1142402,"uid":67549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:57:25.000Z","msg":"呀爸食咗煙好多年，但最近成日都咳，好擔心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前試過拎啲小冊子返嚟俾佢，佢睇都唔睇<br />\nFacebook有啲食煙後果Video特登Tag佢，佢問我做咩Tag佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我直頭同佢講叫佢戒煙，佢就會唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家成日半夜聽到佢咳，唔舒服又唔睇醫生，是旦啪兩粒感冒藥就算<br />\n佢都五張幾，好驚佢有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人成功勸過身邊嘅人戒煙？"},{"pid":"b496cf637592077830765a8dee72ba7f664ad9dd","tid":1142402,"uid":217079,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bcdb2b3c25675c5ec890e83984209ebaa2e10a04","tid":1142402,"uid":67549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:57:25.000Z","msg":"呀爸食咗煙好多年，但最近成日都咳，好擔心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前試過拎啲小冊子返嚟俾佢，佢睇都唔睇<br />\nFacebook有啲食煙後果Video特登Tag佢，佢問我做咩Tag佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我直頭同佢講叫佢戒煙，佢就會唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家成日半夜聽到佢咳，唔舒服又唔睇醫生，是旦啪兩粒感冒藥就算<br />\n佢都五張幾，好驚佢有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人成功勸過身邊嘅人戒煙？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:59:18.000Z","msg":"你屋企會唔會有d小朋友係到？小朋友勸會易d 我都係細過勸阿爸戒最後佢都戒到"},{"pid":"60436f5be2e926a72ee859fb567f38ede6ef2256","tid":1142402,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:59:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ddff3fd7160b57ac73109228b72485bdf71b9aa","tid":1142402,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"